Nuriance is a 54-year-old seasonal farmer. She is married to Marthen who is a 55-year-old breeder. From their marriage, Nuriance and Marthen have been blessed with eight children. Four of the children are married and living with their own families, and the other four are still living with Nuriance. Nuriance's children are: Yohana, 28 years old and married; Robinson, 26 years old and married; Yuliana, 24 years old and married; 
Hesliana, 22 years old and married; Martinus, 21 years old and graduated from Senior high school; Mariance, 20 years old, graduated from Senior high school; Seprianus, 16 years old, in the 1st grade of Senior high school; and Kristina, 13 years old, in the 1st grade of Junior high school. 

In order to support her husband to make a living, Nuriance works every day at her little farm. She started her business by purchasing a plot of land using her own money. She plants mustard greens, water spinach and cassava leaves. She wants to purchase more vegetable plots to grow more vegetables to sell in order to generate more money. In order to do so, she is requesting a loan of IDR 4,000,000 to purchase eight vegetable plots, vegetables seeds, insecticides and fertilizer. She hopes that her loan application will be approved.
